87
00:05:05.670 --> 00:05:06.670
We have to find this ring.

88
00:05:06.670 --> 00:05:08.670
It's the last connection I have with Claire.

89
00:05:08.670 --> 00:05:10.670
Greta's always been shady at work.

90
00:05:10.670 --> 00:05:13.149
I'm pretty sure she did the ring.

91
00:05:13.149 --> 00:05:15.149
That ring is important to us.

92
00:05:15.149 --> 00:05:17.180
I'm giving you one last chance.

93
00:05:17.180 --> 00:05:19.180
Hand it over and I'll let you go.

94
00:05:19.180 --> 00:05:21.180
Oh, I didn't steal the ring.

95
00:05:21.180 --> 00:05:23.180
Ungrateful bitch.

96
00:05:23.180 --> 00:05:26.180
Strip her and search every inch.

97
00:05:26.180 --> 00:05:28.819
I'll do it.

98
00:05:28.819 --> 00:05:35.370
