115
00:06:22.860 --> 00:06:25.860
We don't want to harm your precious health.

116
00:06:25.860 --> 00:06:46.709
Mom, today's mess was really Caleb's fault.

117
00:06:46.709 --> 00:06:48.709
Don't you think we went a little too far?

118
00:06:48.709 --> 00:06:52.060
And that girl. Greta.

119
00:06:52.060 --> 00:06:54.180
Her and her father are heartbreaking.

120
00:06:54.180 --> 00:06:56.180
Especially Greta.

121
00:06:56.180 --> 00:06:58.180
She kind of reminds me of her.

122
00:06:58.180 --> 00:07:01.180
Caleb's ring is his connection to Clara.

123
00:07:01.180 --> 00:07:05.019
It's a symbol of your unity as siblings.

124
00:07:05.019 --> 00:07:07.819
It's too important to lose.

125
00:07:07.819 --> 00:07:09.819
So what if we were a bit harsh?

126
00:07:09.819 --> 00:07:10.819
Greta didn't steal the ring.

127
00:07:10.819 --> 00:07:12.819
