161
00:08:55.139 --> 00:08:57.059
Hey, buddy.

162
00:08:57.059 --> 00:08:58.059
Did you find me that cornea?

163
00:08:58.059 --> 00:08:59.059
Just a reminder.

164
00:08:59.059 --> 00:09:02.059
As you lost the bet, you got to find me that cornea.

165
00:09:02.059 --> 00:09:03.059
If you don't,

166
00:09:03.059 --> 00:09:08.059
well, everyone in LA is going to know tomorrow that Mr. Walker is dishonest and unreliable.

167
00:09:08.059 --> 00:09:09.059
Yeah.

168
00:09:09.059 --> 00:09:10.059
I'm still working on it.

169
00:09:10.059 --> 00:09:11.059
Good, good.

170
00:09:11.059 --> 00:09:12.059
Walker, you're the man in LA.

171
00:09:12.059 --> 00:09:14.059
