216
00:11:35.220 --> 00:11:36.700
Listen to me.

217
00:11:36.700 --> 00:11:38.700
Listen a little bit.

218
00:11:38.700 --> 00:11:47.340
I just want you to be safe and healthy.

219
00:11:47.340 --> 00:11:48.399
Yeah.

220
00:11:48.399 --> 00:11:53.399
If you go rest, hurting yourself and giving up your cornea, I swear to God.

221
00:11:53.399 --> 00:11:56.559
Jump off the roof of this hospital.

222
00:11:56.559 --> 00:11:57.559
It's okay.

223
00:11:57.559 --> 00:11:58.750
I promise.

224
00:11:58.750 --> 00:11:59.750
I promise.

225
00:11:59.750 --> 00:12:01.750
