264
00:14:35.750 --> 00:14:37.750
Just use them more.

265
00:14:37.750 --> 00:14:39.750
This way there won't be any coffee stains.

266
00:14:39.750 --> 00:14:42.750
I want the food to be spotless, or as Dad would get mad at you again.

267
00:14:42.750 --> 00:14:51.240
Mr. Walker, Greta's just a filthy janitor.

268
00:14:51.240 --> 00:14:54.169
Get away from her.

269
00:14:54.169 --> 00:14:56.169
It's just a coincidence.

270
00:14:56.169 --> 00:15:27.299
